MOTIVATION
Major U.S. cities continued to experience
moderate house price hikes.
The Big Apple has drawn millions of
global investors for it’s valuable land
Individual investors lack of handy tools to estimate property
sale value; Overwhelming market information makes it hard
to accurately compare prices
The app helps investors obtain the forecasted house sale
price based on provided house info which empowers them to
make the best decisions in investment
